  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t带黑框眼镜的淫僧到底是怎么回事！他……他对少女究竟做了什么！少女的命运又将如何？<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n“湘西苗女雷氏，貌中人而好歌。大業復興間，寢後見一戴黑框目鏡之僧排闥入。女怪曰：「汝何寺長老？來此何為？」僧曰：「余非凡僧，乃三台寺衲衣佛也，愛卿歌喉，故來相晤，卿從我，當令卿富貴。」女畏懾，欲拒之，而身不能動，遂為輕薄……”<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzY0YTVlMDg2ZmQ4OTc4MDAwMTMzZGZiYw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/64a5e086fd8978000133dfbc\">点击查看该文</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGUyOTE0ZGM3ZmUwYzUxM2M2OTQ3LmpwZz93aWR0aD01NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTM3Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e2914dc7fe0c513c6947.jpg?width=550&amp;height=377\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e2914dc7fe0c513c6947.jpg?width=550&amp;height=377\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4e2914dc7fe0c513c6947.jpg?width=550&amp;height=377\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
